  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  systolic blood pressure &gt;= 140 mmHg

          -  BMI between 18 and 32 kg/m2

          -  apparently healthy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  antihypertensive medication

          -  medically prescribed or slimming diet

          -  lactating, pregnant

          -  irregular pulse
      </textblock>
